prompt.template:
Generate a personalized account-status email for the following customer.
CUSTOMER DATA - Customer Name: ${companyname} - Credit Limit: ${creditlimit} - Standard Payment Terms: ${terms} - Primary Currency: ${currency}
USER INFORMATION ${user}
CONTEXT DATASETS 1. Current Promotions (Doc ID: All Active Promotions) 2. Open Sales Orders & Status (Doc ID: Open Sales Orders for RAG) 3. Items Purchased in the Last 120 Days (Doc Id: Recently Purchased Items - Last 120 Days with Qty)
REQUIREMENTS • Open-order summary: highlight order numbers and current status (e.g., Fulfilled, Pending Billing). • Re-order suggestion: mention 1-2 SKUs from RECENT_ITEMS that are trending low or match seasonal demand. • Promotion: offer at least one promo from PROMOTIONS that fits the customer profile. • Keep the email strictly plain text. • Address the customer by first name if available; otherwise use company name. • Ask some generic questions at the open or indicate a friendly few sentences about business, life, or general pleasantries. Maybe talk about how much you're enjoying experimenting with AI lately. • Close with: “Best regards, [insert user data] ar@yourcompany.com | +1 555-123-4567”
